Paddi Edwards https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paddi_Edwards 0 Patricia Mary Ursula Edwards (March 8, 1931 – October 18, 1999), known as Paddi Edwards, was an English-born American actress. She worked steadily in film and television. Patricia_Mary_Ursula_Edwards ( March_8_,_1931 – October_18_,_1999 ) , known as Paddi_Edwards , was an_English-born_American_actress . She worked steadily in film_and_television .
